<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="flex-1 max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6">Last updated: 12 April 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none text-gray-600 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy">1. Overview</h2>
      <p>CalculatorMate (calculatormate.com.au) is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your data. We comply with the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs) contained in the Privacy Act 1988 (Cth).</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>We do not collect personal information.</strong> Our calculators run entirely in your browser. The numbers you enter into calculators are processed locally on your device and are never sent to our servers or stored anywhere.</p>
      <p>We do collect anonymous usage data through the following services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> — collects anonymous browsing data including pages visited, time spent, device type, and general geographic location (country/city level). No personally identifiable information is collected.</li>
        <li><strong>Server logs</strong> — our web server records IP addresses, browser types, and pages requested for security and performance monitoring. These logs are retained for 30 days and then deleted.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy">3. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Google Analytics cookies</strong> (_ga, _gid) — used to distinguish unique visitors and track sessions. These are first-party cookies set by Google Analytics.</li>
        <li><strong>Amazon affiliate cookies</strong> — when you click an affiliate link to Amazon.com.au, Amazon sets cookies on their domain to track the referral for commission purposes.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not use cookies for advertising targeting, user profiling, or tracking across other websites.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — for anonymous website analytics. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-navy underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — for affiliate product recommendations. <a href="https://www.amazon.com.au/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=468496" class="text-navy underline">Amazon's Privacy Notice</a></li>
        <li><strong>Tailwind CSS (CDN)</strong> — for website styling, served from cdn.tailwindcss.com</li>
        <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — for typography, served from fonts.googleapis.com</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy">5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>Our website is served over HTTPS (TLS encryption). We do not store any user data, calculator inputs, or personal information on our servers. All calculations are performed client-side in your browser.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy">6. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our website is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy">7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under the Australian Privacy Act, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li>Access any personal information we hold about you (we hold none)</li>
        <li>Request correction of any inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Opt out of Google Analytics tracking by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" class="text-navy underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy">9. Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at calculatormate@benslater.me.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

